These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, romance
1. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
City: edinburgh, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| City   | edinburgh | colone |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, goat
1. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | goat |

 #################################

 
